name: Zen Bar Opening Party 🎉 - VIBEY CO-WORKING 🍄🎶
description:
Today is a special day.

Beyond being a full moon, Zuzaluans just unlocked a NEW VENUE for great vibes...

The Zen Bar! Just past the Kiki's (Spilja) Bar, on the way to the Marina Garden.

Gary will be posted up there from 11-4pm playing music of the likes of FKJ, Fred Again, various Amapiano mixes, and select requests :)
